


Configuration Details -
ddl.auto -> create, update, verify
create-> whenever application starts, it creates all new tables and schemas. if application restarts all existing tables and data will be dropped and recreated
update-> everytime you start the application, only the udpate changes are implemented.
Verify->  it does not create/update anything, it just verifies if the DB has all the tables and schemas mentioned in code, if not matching show erros
and won't start the application

Local Development -> Create or Update
Production-> Verify
Generally Tables and schemas are created using seperate script through Flyway,  Liquidbase etc
